<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #07131A; color: #E8F1F8; padding: 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; background: #0F1F2A; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;">
      <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #14E3F7;">MusicFlow</h2>
      <p>Bienvenido. Confirma tu dirección de correo para activar tu cuenta.</p>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
        <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: #14E3F7; color: #07131A; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
          Verificar correo
        </a>
      </p>
      <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #1F3540; margin: 24px 0;" />
      <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #5A6770; text-align: center;">
        © {{year}} MusicFlow
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
